1379
02:01:05,531 --> 02:01:07,969
[CLEARS THROAT]
Call Bonasera.

1380
02:01:08,926 --> 02:01:10,319
I need him now.

1381
02:01:16,151 --> 02:01:18,109
[CONTINUES DIALING]

1382
