1398
02:03:22,190 --> 02:03:27,195
Monday, Tuesday, Thursday,
Wednesday, Friday, Sunday, Saturday.

1399
02:03:27,238 --> 02:03:29,153
[HORN HONKING]

1400
02:03:34,419 --> 02:03:36,508
Greetings, Don Tommasino.

1401
02:03:36,552 --> 02:03:38,467
How are things in Palermo?

1402
02:03:44,603 --> 02:03:48,564
Michael is teaching me to
drive. Watch, I'll show you.

1403
02:03:51,436 --> 02:03:53,612
How are things in Palermo?

1404
02:03:53,656 --> 02:03:57,399
Young people don't respect
anything any more...

1405
02:03:57,442 --> 02:03:59,923
Times are changing
for the worse.

1406
02:04:03,492 --> 02:04:06,799
This place has become
too dangerous for you.

1407
02:04:09,585 --> 02:04:14,764
I want you to move to a villa
near Siracusa, right now.

1408
02:04:19,986 --> 02:04:21,858
What's wrong?

1409
02:04:23,033 --> 02:04:25,209
Bad news from America.

1410
02:04:26,906 --> 02:04:31,389
Your brother, Santino,
they killed him.

1411
02:04:34,958 --> 02:04:36,525
[CAR HONKING]

1412
02:04:36,568 --> 02:04:37,961
[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

1413
02:04:38,004 --> 02:04:39,832
Let's go... you promised.

1414
02:04:58,199 --> 02:04:59,504
Fabrizio! [SPEAKS ITALIAN]

1415
02:04:59,548 --> 02:05:01,202
Get the car.

1416
02:05:02,420 --> 02:05:05,119
Are you driving
yourself, boss? Yes.

1417
02:05:05,162 --> 02:05:07,251
Is your wife
coming with you?

1418
02:05:07,295 --> 02:05:10,036
No, I want you to take her to her father's
house until I know things are safe.

1419
02:05:10,080 --> 02:05:11,908
Okay, anything
you say, boss.

1420
02:05:16,956 --> 02:05:18,262
[BOTH SPEAKING ITALIAN]

1421
02:05:18,306 --> 02:05:20,830
Calo, where is Apollonia?

1422
02:05:20,873 --> 02:05:24,225
She's going to surprise you.
She wants to drive.

1423
02:05:26,618 --> 02:05:30,056
She'll make a good
American wife.

1424
02:05:30,100 --> 02:05:32,581
Wait. I'll get the baggage.

1425
02:05:42,373 --> 02:05:43,505
Fabrizio!

1426
02:05:45,115 --> 02:05:46,856
Where are you going?

1427
02:05:46,899 --> 02:05:48,510
[CAR HONKING]
[APOLLONIA SPEAKS ITALAIN]

1428
02:05:48,553 --> 02:05:50,512
I'll drive you.
Wait there

1429
02:05:56,866 --> 02:05:58,389
